Hello @faic! Thanks for updating the PR.

 - In the file [`pandas/compat/__init__.py`](https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/1dc417e00ad6338ce181b9636c8e6911363d7f1b/pandas/compat/__init__.py), following are the PEP8 issues :

> [Line 61:1](https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/1dc417e00ad6338ce181b9636c8e6911363d7f1b/pandas/compat/__init__.py#L61): [E402](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=pep8%20E402) module level import not at top of file
> [Line 174:5](https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/1dc417e00ad6338ce181b9636c8e6911363d7f1b/pandas/compat/__init__.py#L174): [E731](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=pep8%20E731) do not assign a lambda expression, use a def
> [Line 221:1](https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/1dc417e00ad6338ce181b9636c8e6911363d7f1b/pandas/compat/__init__.py#L221): [E305](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=pep8%20E305) expected 2 blank lines after class or function definition, found 1
> [Line 245:80](https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/1dc417e00ad6338ce181b9636c8e6911363d7f1b/pandas/compat/__init__.py#L245): [E501](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=pep8%20E501) line too long (90 > 79 characters)
> [Line 278:9](https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/1dc417e00ad6338ce181b9636c8e6911363d7f1b/pandas/compat/__init__.py#L278): [E722](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=pep8%20E722) do not use bare except'
> [Line 297:80](https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/1dc417e00ad6338ce181b9636c8e6911363d7f1b/pandas/compat/__init__.py#L297): [E501](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=pep8%20E501) line too long (90 > 79 characters)
> [Line 337:1](https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/1dc417e00ad6338ce181b9636c8e6911363d7f1b/pandas/compat/__init__.py#L337): [E305](https://duckduckgo.com/?q=pep8%20E305) expected 2 blank lines after class or function definition, found 1
